      <title>Alphinity Investment 的全球市场 Jonker</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-06/alphinity-investment-s-jonker-on-global-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphinity Investment 的客户投资组合经理兼投资专家 Elfreda Jonker 讨论了她对全球市场的展望和投资策略，并解释了她对电动汽车持谨慎态度的原因。她在“澳大利亚黎明”节目中与安娜贝尔·德鲁勒斯和海迪·斯特劳德-瓦茨进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-06/alphinity-investment-s-jonker-on-global-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:36:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国顶级对冲基金半夏减持股票以求在溃败中“生存”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/top-chinese-hedge-fund-banxia-slashes-stocks-for-survival-in-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国一家顶级宏观对冲基金表示，随着中国市场跌势加深，该基金上个月削减了股票头寸，在承认押注经济快速复苏的错误后蒙受了损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/top-chinese-hedge-fund-banxia-slashes-stocks-for-survival-in-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:32:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>干旱过后产量下滑，泰国食糖前景恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/thailand-s-sugar-outlook-worsens-as-yields-slide-after-dry-spell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于干旱天气影响植物生长，泰国本季食糖产量预计将低于预期，这将挤压全球供应，并可能延续基准期货的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/thailand-s-sugar-outlook-worsens-as-yields-slide-after-dry-spell</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:03:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通预计中国将采取更多市场刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-06/jpmorgan-sees-more-market-stimulus-measures-from-china-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产管理公司全球市场策略师Marcella Chow讨论了中国股票、经济和政府政策。据知情人士透露，中国正在收紧对国内机构投资者以及一些离岸单位的交易限制，当局正在努力阻止股市进一步暴跌。周在“彭博市场：中国公开赛”上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-06/jpmorgan-sees-more-market-stimulus-measures-from-china-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:14:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于股市暴跌，中国保证金债务自 2016 年以来降幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/china-margin-debt-sees-biggest-drop-since-2016-amid-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济衰退加剧引发了杠杆头寸急于平仓，中国股票交易保证金债务出现自 2016 年初以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/china-margin-debt-sees-biggest-drop-since-2016-amid-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 01:57:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
